dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data layer represents address locations for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Lincoln_Addresses_2016.gdb.[These are the point locations of the site addresses in Lincoln County.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data set provides a point location for every site address in the county.]
